version 1.1.0, Apr 10, 2014
--------------------------
+ Added "Off mode"
+ Added separate tollerances for different modes
* Reference values are autosaved
* Fixed all known issues (e.g. freezing flags values
  after switching monitoring mode)
* Binary monitoring operates with full set of PVs (MonitFlg, ArchFlg, Arch)
* ENABLED & CH_FLG should be provided to dedicated Monit*.db (not *Common.db)